      "overview": "B\u00c1U V\u1eacT TR\u1edcI CHO is an emotionally rich, heartwarming film that celebrates family bonds for T\u1ebft 2026. Ng\u1ecdc (Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Anh \u0110\u00e0o), a single mother who conceived her child through donor insemination, takes a seaside getaway to escape her past. There, she and her son T\u00f4 unexpectedly encounter H\u1ed3ng (Tu\u1ea5n Tr\u1ea7n), a free-spirited fisherman who happens to be the donor behind T\u00f4\u2019s birth. This awkward reunion draws three strangers into a series of humorous yet tense situations as everything spirals beyond control. Is this \u201cheaven-sent\u201d father a destined gift, or merely life\u2019s cruel twist of fate?",
